README
======

These document templates are provided as examples that
you could use to start your Progress Report for the
Major/Minor Project (MMP). You are not required to use these 
templates, but they might be a useful starting point. 

Word Template
The Word example is provided as a Word template. Double click to 
open in Word. This will create a new unnamed document based on this
template. 

LaTeX Template 
A style file, mmpProgressReport.sty contains the main formatting information. The 
document MMP_ProgressReport_example.tex shows an example
of how to use the template. You will specific certain information near
to the start of the file, which will be used to create the title page 
information and the headers and footers. 

The example also shows the use of a BibTeX file and how to include it 
and make references. 

